List of abstracts -> i select a few abstracts -> send email

422 error
```json
{
  "webargs_errors": {
    "sender_address": [
      "Missing data for required field."
    ]
  }
}
```


THE PAYLOAD SENT IS THIS

```json
{"from_address":"amministrazione@domain.example","subject":"eaqaffas","body":"<p>Gentile {first_name},<br><br><br><br>Cordiali saluti<br>admin admin</p>","bcc_addresses":[],"copy_for_sender":false,"recipient_roles":["submitter"],"abstract_id":[9,11]}
```

but the api is expecting this

```json
{"sender_address":"amministrazione@domain.example","subject":"eaqaffas","body":"<p>Gentile {first_name},<br><br><br><br>Cordiali saluti<br>admin admin</p>","bcc_addresses":[],"copy_for_sender":false,"recipient_roles":["submitter"],"abstract_id":[9,11]}
```

A couple of fixes for the CSC:
- Sorting seems to be broken (we should show the results in proper order);
- If possible, it would be nice to include the session name as a prefix of each question (since otherwise it may be impossible to differentiate them). Or at least some sort of ID that lets them see what the result actually relates to.

